{"tid":2414744,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"新手跟左GME風入市 依家開始懷疑人生 半個月既心路歷程","createTime":"2021-02-19T15:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T06:29:23.000Z","uid":30836,"like":4,"dislike":108,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"bc83d544d0502de097fe200f99b2d97f502aa34d","tid":2414744,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"利申 兩萬HKD 本暫時翻咗十八倍 半工讀學生<br />\n<br />\n唔太影響生活但呢半個月感覺受左好多挫折<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣見到GME個勢頭好勁 就走去FT開AC<br />\n<br />\n期間睇住GME 40幾上到 60-70<br />\n<br />\n到開到戶嗰下就抱住唔好執輸既心態去ALL IN<br />\n<br />\n期間上到420 放咗<br />\n<br />\n但都仲懷抱緊信念其他巴打會一齊走<br />\n<br />\n呢個時間就ALL IN咗啲CCIV<br />\n<br />\n25蚊入左CCIV 之後無再睇呢隻野<br />\n<br />\n去到今朝起身望左望CCIV 個人完全係崩撚潰<br />\n<br />\n如果當初買多啲 依家就可以財自退休<br />\n<br />\n當然我知無「如果」呢件事 但呢下真係好懷疑自己既心態同眼光<br />\n<br />\n贏既錢真係唔多但懷疑自己係咪適合繼續玩股票<br />\n<br />\n係咪真係注定打多半世工<br />\n<br />\n好想搵地方發洩<br />\n<br />\n最後祝大家贏多啲 呢篇文當笑話睇下就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b930f1391055c119ef2ff8c9b578cfba09d457","tid":2414744,"uid":279640,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:55:31.000Z","msg":"你贏咗錢喎"},{"pid":"b3ea67b714023ded6265b8c672a73158d6cb63a0","tid":2414744,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n妖股日日有<br />\n下次囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb51e97121d6d0fca5fb1eac09616246932b34c","tid":2414744,"uid":189638,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"56b930f1391055c119ef2ff8c9b578cfba09d457","tid":2414744,"uid":279640,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:55:31.000Z","msg":"你贏咗錢喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"佢意思係贏到懷疑人生"},{"pid":"449e6496af861dafad6a00d583ba5973af5043ff","tid":2414744,"uid":89337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T15:58:37.000Z","m